From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: RK3588 AMDGPU Bringup <noreply@example.com>
Date: Fri, 13 Mar 2026 22:40:00 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] drm/amdgpu/discovery: include PSP IP block for RLC backdoor
 load type

On gfx_v10, the RLC backdoor path consumes `adev->psp.toc`. If discovery skips
PSP IP initialization for `AMDGPU_FW_LOAD_RLC_BACKDOOR_AUTO`, TOC remains empty
and autoload cannot start.
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_discovery.c | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_discovery.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_discovery.c
index 55b7b3a70444..0f5e2e3a147d 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_discovery.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_discovery.c
@@ -2381,7 +2381,8 @@ int amdgpu_discovery_set_ip_blocks(struct amdgpu_device *adev)
 			if (r)
 				return r;
 
-			if (likely(adev->firmware.load_type == AMDGPU_FW_LOAD_PSP)) {
+			if (likely(adev->firmware.load_type == AMDGPU_FW_LOAD_PSP ||
+				   adev->firmware.load_type == AMDGPU_FW_LOAD_RLC_BACKDOOR_AUTO)) {
 				r = amdgpu_discovery_set_psp_ip_blocks(adev);
 				if (r)
 					return r;
-- 
2.43.0

